{"tid":1212183,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(突發) 美國國會本周將提出《香港人權與民主法案》2","createTime":"2019-06-12T17:36:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T04:53:39.000Z","uid":134294,"like":52,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"f186bce11b298938c5114619d65100c137854991","tid":1212183,"uid":134294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T17:36:29.000Z","msg":"《香港人權與民主法案》法案目的, 是對涉及鎮壓香港基本自由的香港或中國大陸的政府官員，設立懲罰機制，包括禁止涉事官員入境美國及凍結其在美國之資產.<br />\n<br />\nJim McGovern係美國國會和行政當局中國委員會（CECC）既主席.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/RepMcGovern/status/1138824083985113088\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FRepMcGovern%2Fstatus%2F1138824083985113088&d=0lytrcPBTEnksf4YR0ybMc%2BxtiM4uRDursPVmWLIdz4%3D&h=6bfe50ab\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FRepMcGovern%2Fstatus%2F1138824083985113088&h=d5d83370\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/RepMcGovern/status/1138824083985113088</a><br />\n<br />\nRep. Jim McGovern<br />\n&rlm;Verified account @RepMcGovern<br />\n<br />\n1/ I'm proud to stand with the people of #HongKong. Passage of the #ExtraditionLaw would put Hong Kong human rights advocates, business persons, journalists and American citizens at risk of rendition to mainland #China<br />\n<br />\n2/ I urge Chief Executive #CarrieLam &amp; #LegCo President #AndrewLeung to withdraw the current bill and explore alternatives that preserve #HongKong&rsquo;s autonomy and protect human rights and the rule of law.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3/ As the people of #HongKong continue peaceful demonstrations, the Police Commissioner and Secretary for Security should direct #HongKong police to refrain from using excessive force and intimidation and I urge them to protect the right to free expression.<br />\n<br />\n4/ Strong protections for human rights and rule of law are the foundation of Hong Kong&rsquo;s prosperity &amp; flourishing U.S.-Hong Kong relations. If the extradition law passes, Congress must look to revise the Hong Kong Policy Act of 1992 to reflect the erosion of autonomy.<br />\n<br />\n5/5 This week I will join @marcorubio &amp; @RepChrisSmith in introducing the &ldquo;HK Human Rights &amp; Democracy Act&rdquo; to reaffirm U.S. commitment to human rights &amp; the rule of law at a time when Hong Kong&rsquo;s autonomy is imperiled by Chinese gov't interference &amp; a revised #ExtraditionLaw.<br />\n推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e824f06ea6a6a7afda30e218bc213d5465c80b40","tid":1212183,"uid":69139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T17:36:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"343515c8bf08566a4210305b4d903e81d181f9f9","tid":1212183,"uid":134294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T17:37:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b15f7d31c2809002db672064dfb7a0237525a864","tid":1212183,"uid":134294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T17:41:28.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"b1a76aebf1517feeb866536e88dcf77ae29bdc40","tid":1212183,"uid":45613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T17:43:30.000Z","msg":"Thank you<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nIt is urgent"},{"pid":"e05746b582da5e1970de8a470136cacbd9257f3f","tid":1212183,"uid":1882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T17:46:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e84d2b3f6c57510f2759fd100495b71340b819c","tid":1212183,"uid":124048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T17:48:05.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"3de19c8c9f6ec5430dd2c7d7fbdea02fca74a41a","tid":1212183,"uid":135334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T17:48:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e915365f8f218183b442fd13323327b193c2a5f1","tid":1212183,"uid":5710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T17:54: